"hg backout --merge REV1" at REV2 below implies steps below:

(1) update to REV1 (REV2 => REV1)
(2) revert by REV1^1
(3) commit backing out revision (REV3)
(4) update to REV2 (REV3 => REV2)
(5) merge with REV3 (REV2 => REV2, REV3)

